# Keep the build context small and reproducible: never copy host-built artifacts
# or VCS metadata. The db-lib submodule SOURCE (src/prisma/package.json) is kept
# so the image can build its dist/ itself; its node_modules/dist are excluded via
# the wildcards below (the deps stage rebuilds them).
node_modules
**/node_modules
dist
**/dist
.git
**/.git
*.log
npm-debug.log*
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
coverage
.vscode
.idea
